<SYNC Start=486143><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=486919><P Class=ENCC>
You know about the plate thing?
<SYNC Start=489513><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=489722><P Class=ENCC>
Oh, yeah, yeah. No,<br>
Joey doesn't share food.
<SYNC Start=492213><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=492391><P Class=ENCC>
I mean, just last week<br>
we were having breakfast..
<SYNC Start=495121><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=495328><P Class=ENCC>
and he had a couple grapes<br>
on his plate.
<SYNC Start=497353><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=497530><P Class=ENCC>
- You wouldn't let her have a grape?<br>
- No, not me.
<SYNC Start=499794><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=499966><P Class=ENCC>
Emma.
<SYNC Start=501331><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=504103><P Class=ENCC>
Joey doesn't share food!
<SYNC Start=506901><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=511277><P Class=ENCC>
Well, I still think that is a stupid reason<br>
not to call someone again.
<SYNC Start=514713><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=514881><P Class=ENCC>
You are calling her, okay?
<SYNC Start=517145><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=517316><P Class=ENCC>
And if you need to, then just<br>
get an extra plate of fries for the table.
<SYNC Start=520877><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=525625><P Class=ENCC>
I like that.
<SYNC Start=527286><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=527460><P Class=ENCC>
