<SYNC Start=569735><P Class=ENCC>
Oh, this place is great!
<SYNC Start=572363><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=574340><P Class=ENCC>
Okay, you guys have fun.<br>
I'm gonna go talk to people in this voice.
<SYNC Start=578743><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=579779><P Class=ENCC>
Rach, come on, I'm not gonna wear<br>
any of this. Nothing silver.
<SYNC Start=583146><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=583316><P Class=ENCC>
- Why?<br>
